<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

    <head>
        <title>News &amp; Announcements | Midwest Alliance for Applied Genomic Epidemiology</title>
        <%- include('../head') %>
    </head>

    <body class="claro patric <% if (request.isAuthenticated && request.isAuthenticated()) { %>Authenticated<% } %>">
        <div id="ApplicationContainer" data-dojo-type="dijit/layout/BorderContainer" class="layoutContainer"
            data-dojo-props="id:'ApplicationContainer',gutters:false,liveSplitters:false">
            <%- include('../navbar') %>
            <div data-dojo-type="dijit/layout/ContentPane" data-dojo-props="region:'center'"
                style="padding:0px;border:0px solid #ddd;background:inherit;">
                <div id="bv-brc-page">
                    <div id="bv-brc-page-container" style="width:100%;">
                        <div class="page-content" style="width:80%; margin: 0 auto; text-align:left;">
                            <style>
                                h1 {
                                    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
                                    font-weight: 600;
                                    margin: 0;
                                    padding: 0;
                                }

                                p {
                                    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
                                    font-weight: 400;
                                    font-size: 16px;
                                    line-height: 1.5;
                                }
                            </style>
                            <div class="max-w-[75%] mx-auto">
                                <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold font-poppins pt-4 pb-6">Announcements</h1>

                                <!-- Announcement 1 -->
                                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-white shadow-sm">
                                    <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium bg-maage-secondary-100 text-maage-secondary-700 rounded px-2 py-0.5 mb-3">Announcement</span>
                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold font-poppins mb-2">Public Launch of the MAAGE Platform</h2>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Coming Soon</p>
                                    <p>We are excited to announce the upcoming public launch of the Midwest Alliance for Applied Genomic Epidemiology (MAAGE) platform. MAAGE provides state and local public health agencies with cutting-edge genomic surveillance tools to support infectious disease response across the Midwest. Stay tuned for the official launch date and more details.</p>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Announcement 2 -->
                                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-white shadow-sm">
                                    <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium bg-maage-secondary-100 text-maage-secondary-700 rounded px-2 py-0.5 mb-3">Webinar</span>
                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold font-poppins mb-2">Webinar: Introduction to MAAGE</h2>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Date &amp; Time: TBD</p>
                                    <p>Join us for an introductory webinar covering the core features of the MAAGE platform, including genomic surveillance workflows, data visualization tools, and how public health professionals can leverage MAAGE for pathogen monitoring and outbreak investigation. Registration details will be announced soon.</p>
                                </div>

                                <!-- Announcement 3 -->
                                <div class="border border-gray-200 rounded-lg p-6 mb-6 bg-white shadow-sm">
                                    <span class="inline-block text-xs font-medium bg-maage-secondary-100 text-maage-secondary-700 rounded px-2 py-0.5 mb-3">Workshop</span>
                                    <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold font-poppins mb-2">Workshop: Genomic Epidemiology Using MAAGE</h2>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-3">Date &amp; Location: TBD</p>
                                    <p>This hands-on workshop will guide participants through applied genomic epidemiology workflows using the MAAGE platform. Topics will include sequence analysis, phylogenetic interpretation, AMR profiling, and integrating genomic data into public health decision-making. More details on registration and logistics will be shared as they become available.</p>
                                </div>

                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <%- include('../footer') %>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('../javascript') %>
    </body>

</html>